;一项采矿法案，政府承诺以“特朗普的速度”振兴该行业并&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/r2smQWDtPMluruqoUJvIM59UZa7L2_u3reORB60jRWhBEuiySBgGFhFbtmeMgeTuI-RM9WDS_5wFLnMWTjB7hHa9aUF-Ts6wh6-iFNBFVh8YM2gnLCLbtzToSEHVWL0NKWYmTg9OEfrKsS87AqJj9h-Vy3rFi6lEepdLxld-fqgBE_s7Rec8HmCMf3qdmABUf9lgsjECIyYhY_eOF_-gX5Z_4pepaDXcdZaX6reRo22TTbag88A8moEaqdEfI59-y22wX0jADp1i_DYPmimtVrG-hD13rUudjSe6lzV0xBob8LZOjW8xDMMYoBWReNyakZKJFtxqvjXpN73AcYMSXTst2tjRpWUurmHCff8lA3ohy7FkgS1U10ROBfI/2kCU9HufzQOvOGFni57iLdopGEmiDfWX/18" target="_blank"&gt;吸引外国投资&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;这是继特朗普在一月份推翻前总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗之后，委内瑞拉和美国之间经济和政治关系升温的最新迹象&lt;/strong&gt;。上周，在内政部长道格·布尔古姆访问后不久，双方同意&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/mrpX8sNDPPGkwQz2d8r4g-PFb_mSnGFyE7yj1woTl9iKnJLyMsj_07R6rVQ01mWoG6IIrpk5RYz_b1X6RVsG4NXk7gzaH3vFFSHNhFUkzp6LHfI31bKlySryvgy2hZ1yC0vKu6wkdwbKiTmw1EX6E21yEOIwnjsFqQ2lnVFzCEMb__5iCKkJCF7fT4v7f-GykQpKfNeVAe2pKZkOXxJ1Y0M0Cgj3i_lzS4fm8rS3pJeOpRLsFrHFbSrGyKwjaiQqpMa1z0tjfLMdWdkzDNNS8kCwa3bXVVbsE2CXYx2vT151mjjA3v7RsBa0pSFkgGcCNaC56GN7wDHFfMRR6-g8TVJYXkEZcWm1L8Ji43lYPK2xHMcRhD7mrCCj39A/pqfGOwfCMvNGqz3eqPFZ9OHsrW_lOUtC/18" target="_blank"&gt;恢复外交关系&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;采矿法案&lt;/strong&gt;以一月份的类似立法为基础，当时委内瑞拉立法者批准了对其长达数十年的民族主义石油政策的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/J8J0oQ_HQdeKWtBthXJ6N8aXJ9SQ4Ah6dXKUF1p4tjNHLExooGmc2uG9SctSAZzWgtXph3DC8wWDleYbvVC34-SH-OclZp4bEBQ0CxHFMVBU-MymfRxkuyiVAB2_AmA9VUt6l4ZS49xFUpuz3GBcsAFhzq0bSekxrTUXqDyidg05EFqrMiO5fwjR8rRzEgK47ZOn9imXJKdtC4IewaPYWghij5bZc0rz_YE5uL4uSfV-IDUbQSC3S_3H4S8-larYYKZFz3D5hlLq5QJarJkRmLSAgRrEhCeicPYmt8Z2qhZI25fuXMm-lc-jaQt6qOrFWrKtx-bO5buoysq3Q9eVSgcfG0IjDMkkaJChdYBTGSEX3-8MhGHVKr2D_oA/k1zc0i1K2dnEA74DyPl9Ibfwv7RZ2NFP/18" target="_blank"&gt;历史性改革&lt;/a&gt;，赋予官员广泛的自由裁量权来调整税收和特许权使用费以吸引私人资本。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;外国投资者&lt;/strong&gt;已经为这一转变做好了准备。特朗普政府颁发许可证，允许雪佛龙、壳牌和英国石油等&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/6vaC2VyKqMMkaRjKyOEzZOjMPfYlFpTBLieMpcpFVhCZ6uCZ43gU6y0FpYoHMgBvLScPm-D5tUGHpjSGoGtZgvAdWmkxO30nGGSkvPGkKTHUByJyX0cykjj-4YA0prykVKykaZzzK1BrUeaMQLYmmHz3IdcBiOhN2GowvK0VAgrG0k-FL9TdCl3ypreSL2T2ZEgnefv2WsLuudGTFgrgqcR8t--OGfBk0z7zX8dDxRfoA8wbgKoH0O7Nwr7DgWBrd-n53ojQhMaWn29TsQlDRMB1gdOX16cYr-KipcKHV8uxgBFWkFH3FML_K5VC6t6PzkCS5F9kvlubgCOIbPPKAs2itrZpanDkd2jkL5UMl0OJ0X6gPmDqtpGJOPs/hMN0ZUz0OSVmO4e3WUBM_SiHdEJUb7u_/18" target="_blank"&gt;西方石油公司&lt;/a&gt;在委内瑞拉运营。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/zQW2W0oMpwFUHwrfxDYZSWg5cJRlKXvRVoW-kGxBHeM3cSHClgC5qudoYFIm1lMsDqC31620WxpSQRpfrF2fywtrHKYJmp6K-Or6ryjMLZ6zT6-QzrBfU3zvErXMhh0ICBjTQ1niD3eufvC5ssS2cYeEAV9DI8xepfQGXUN-AWMPpulXrxD0vTMCSfShCLC9a3R6C8OUfz2opF8iNLJyQ6AySBLLDDh2DXfJQfblqXtPF8lCKwL4j6-PJPFVR8BQkfvsNJ5ybgNaoPT0WUtZDFFv4eqEJ35srkcen6mIquWVEWSZMO7yDNjQxp_6oNzTE442Hg3x4DzkvBqB0CgKc097Y4Urzu_GZD2R5XWTo5daLnBBMa5X0jjbIOk/dWgcGzBcKDI7oL7Zz-MKeAUQZpRnKQAx/18" target="_blank"&gt;让我们来看看&lt;/a&gt;特朗普对委内瑞拉石油工业的计划是否现实。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;大事&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/BMhTJlJhC_VYLaDStSdQAN6LAJyF37qOR2dABRpBZTaWRSTeP