XrBQtZdXWVyIp-59uRBPPJP2OY6Xo/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;在此处&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;注册&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;。&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;对于伊朗战争，唐纳德·特朗普并没有太多值得欢呼的地方，越来越多的迹象表明他低估了伊朗伊斯兰共和国的韧性。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;过去 24 小时的两个主要事态发展只会增加美国的挫败感，并给总统带来结束冲突在中东和全球市场造成的屠杀的压力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;首先，伊朗最高级的神职人员&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/meqIDcsB0_TSdkZmZ-9MY7zNpz7eP_YUNZaK32vdQEPcT6hKG37loiXM_466hUaIhkNyHTdQVvRGA59vMAkUdrigDKLANi2Xm6VIVb-4jMjOifWUMs56dXnDC7Rp0bZ_E2pbAqIVUwN2ZfYp8OL2p38liM_aXdSCClSJGQJYBmLdUvV5MLLq8VEJV2FuyJnKFJHwQh-GYRNUp1rViWPzl0MzB4jPoi87vdR3tI2HBY0eIrIEIB3a21csYVlufNLvxU1ul2FqhDNmcAfZi96EpUsjJVQQ3wJ0fxSsJXBh9Y7eaKQ0-yLhgJd_1-qX7osPsSjU08UXGv0tEerzeo8FMQ-f-EvqBlahfDS5vRU7qmdCj7-a9LOjUgrmJLu0vlnb98rBfJ6kkdkEkHZBqoLPpEz79daJ6tFXvEtFxyxxPePScE0OLVdaJ9Gx-Sn9AwIBKkDz9t9JE85409cE1m5GNbiwj7rFY-INCipcOdQ9gYoafmMvEOQfsIiQDhUZEuRP1B1tAx4lZd6hccGQ3__sxA/P_FJO-mG2ibW9BrmwwYiBqwII1kQI9Lb/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普淡化石油飙升，哈梅内伊之子在伊朗掌权"&gt;反抗他&lt;/a&gt;，选择被暗杀的阿里·哈梅内伊的强硬派儿子莫杰塔巴·哈梅内伊为&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Bbhfarqx5LB2jPdtPW6m7prNnnTTNDCyMAPDdYU0moIN5yJXjJxdP5oC83xaCuPe-dJYuYGkDQpp8pMa4LXmsZoVAll0h5olnchFjAYsHN6bP67mWM3jmAx-K3pvBvz9fgHAHj_K_X3mRH3uIghreNEDYfXbB1PN9Sjm9LKs3s_wbM_8qjfWGrn8BxNuXDpPSWb3Ffa5uXs4-kUSyOhp-hwscERm3bY-SVBURdpMMJbau8Ee-NSzeKG0aEGMPi_FTMjiL72D-jtlXoK_Ah4j-TKEXppShBaQljZ9pQw9y8VAZR8Ia8duPIQzU9Jrcj2X0ip9G2YvR3gYZPJaCwhCxJK5uZc2_imxUMWDjSVJ4FfOyj6d5w8Voyrh6_POA1IAK9x7v34KHSHI8_qtOMZSPULsoHjwrQFTxtZLDbAkROF8Z9A2wz1JkpvRWHWVilXMJvL14CzAtytfjlmJlYQdaPmTZbVYXenFJzjOtIbKsYhOfbTJuqHMFu56kfLggY1JWY_2rgFOJFBD8fJtMY6pO6g0LFu1qszr/DncqjKMjU-oyydtjFZabr6vJH1ZcGNFs/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inh